Shopify's paginate functionality relies on the "?page=#" in the url. To force paginate to give you a certain set of results, you MUST have it in the url request.

In clothes collections:
 - If there is only one colorway:
  = Pic 1 is of the actual item
  = All further pictures can be misc pictures
  = Last Pic is a gif
 - If there are more than one colorway
  = Pic 1 is a combination showing numerous colors in a group
  = Pic 2 -> however many colors are of the actual colors of the item in order of the variant layout
  = All further pictures can be misc pictures
  = Last Pic is a gif